summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 11E page 54, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in portion of Lot 3 lying south of line 100 ft. south of and parallel to south margin of Market St. and Lots 4-7, incl., Block 83, Lots 3-28 incl., Block 82, Lots 4-19 incl., Block 80, Lots 1-10, incl., and Lots 17-22 incl., Block 81, Lots 4-13 incl., Block 78, all in Gilman Park Addition.
